color: gold;\">(1327 USD/oz)</span><span style=\"color: red;\">(SP500: 1681)</span>, 聯儲局決定暫緩減購計劃. 同年12月<span style=\"color: gold;\">(1205 USD/oz)</span><span style=\"color: red;\">(SP500: 1848)</span>, 宣佈將於在2014年1月執行減購. 最後2014年10月<span style=\"color: gold;\">(1172 USD/oz)</span><span style=\"color: red;\">(SP500: 2018)</span>, 中止了全部購債活動. 此時聯儲局資產總表達4.5萬億美元."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係黃金價格同股市趨勢一樣 股跌黃金都跌 股升黃金升？<br />\n<br />\n巴打係幾時入GLD架？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:58:45.000Z","msg":"QE 下中長期所有資產價格一定升<br />\n只是金價在股市見底前後  升幅會相對強勢<br />\n但長遠回報一定輸給股市<br />\n<br />\n154入左 GLD"},{"pid":"f6954c87d43d1be084dab5872a8319c941cece46","tid":1945384,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"200股GLD @142<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9b93249fa247cd321eec9261c0a9d03a5917c4","tid":1945384,"uid":271892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4585851f831e61960ad788b11237673e7d3c8a1","tid":1945384,"uid":16664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b11fa2b93cfb3986fa6d86a63e9ad509fb7bfe9b","tid":1945384,"uid":271892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"69c9fe43ae5fe4ed910bbab082926c22a57ed697","tid":1945384,"uid":16664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"買債唔考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"之前都有考慮過<br />\n點驚有債務危機<br />\n<br />\n巴打 點睇債務"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"個人覺得好過買金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T05:04:2